{"id": 513, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对日式杂货店的印象是啥样的？", "description": "价廉物美，吗？", "record_count": 1678, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183812krP5I81Z7CthydA4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-07T01:07:29Z", "questions": [{"id": 414, "title": "你对日式杂货店的印象是啥样的？", "content": "你对日式杂货店的印象是啥样的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 10171, "content": "两元店升级版，但感觉更精致点", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193254N9rYAcGKW8Qdx7VZ.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10172, "content": "设计简单可爱，放在家里也不是很掉份儿", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183231EZvzui5JePSbjpBo.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10173, "content": "永远可以挖出一些你觉得竟然还有这样的东西的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183231bLaX3I2f0KgrhCP8.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10174, "content": "有些明星单品还不错，下手前最好还是做点功课", "image": "img/option/option/201606071932546wgvOHCF3szdk2iN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10175, "content": "不贵但实用的少，论性价比的话并不高", "image": "img/option/option/201606071932543emaMZhVTQd1yAkb.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10176, "content": "有些就是山寨吧，不像真的日本品牌", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193255li896vmV1nBqTrOC.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10178, "content": "感觉开在大商场里还挺违和的", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193255aEpmLS9zq7HFl3i4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 10179, "content": "没逛过，但每次经过都感觉门店总是人很多的样子", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193255x3uh0vLqaU9BSO5F.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}